input_str: A kook is someone who writes or produces articles and materials that seem completely detached from reality. The kook has had a vision of the world that’s different from yours or mine, so different and so compelling that he feels he must tell the world about it, loudly and repeatedly, often with the implication that if he doesn’t get his message across we’re all somehow doomed.
